SUMMARY:reconnect with soo kim <2026-06-18 Thu>
DESCRIPTION:send this text re: the river - here’s a clip from that movie I 
 was\n telling you about that Kerry Tribe made about LA River which I did\n
  sound and music for -(she also made me ride the whole thing with her\n on
  a bike for research purposes).\n <https://www.1301pe.com/news/2018/9/28/k
 erry-tribe-exquisite-corpse-screening-at-descanso-gardens-for-the-group-ex
 hibition-la-reina-de-los-ngeles>
