  be\nlovely to catch up after that" — and the 6/25 reply deliberately left
 \nit open.  Don't wait for her to ping: propose a *specific* day (coffee\n
 or studio visit in the pentagonal ring)\, per the plan's beat (3). Also\nr
 e-raise the Aphasia "Together" clip if the password is still\nunresolved.
